Magnesium Lithospermate B, the main constituent of the Injection of DanShenDuoFenSuanYan (the Injection of Depsides Salts From Salvia Miltiorrhiza), is the active ingredient of Salvia Miltiorrhiza.

 This study record clinical use of The injection of DanShenDuoFenSuanYan in the real world, and observe the adverse drug reactions/ adverse drug events during treatment.

